    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> to a large bowl with your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and gently toss until the salad is coated</p><p>Season the <strong>fried eggs</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> tortilla pizza </strong>topped with the <strong>fried eggs</strong> and the <strong>salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
